      "heading": "讚美耶和華"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Praise the Lord! I will thank the Lord with all my heart as I meet with his godly people. "
